<indexterm><primary>PostCSS</primary></indexterm>

<para><anchor xml:id="_md_node__modules_2postcss_2_r_e_a_d_m_e_1autotoc_md678"/> </para>

<para>PostCSS is a tool for transforming styles with JS plugins. These plugins can lint your CSS, support variables and mixins, transpile future CSS syntax, inline images, and more.</para>

<para>PostCSS is used by industry leaders including Wikipedia, Twitter, Alibaba, and JetBrains. The <link xlink:href="https://github.com/postcss/autoprefixer">Autoprefixer</link> and <link xlink:href="https://stylelint.io/">Stylelint</link> PostCSS plugins is one of the most popular CSS tools.</para>

